OL,3,CThousands of Next retailer workers win
OL,4,Clandmark equal pay claim
OL,6,FThe ruling comes after Next failed to
OL,7,Fprove that the higher wages it paid to
OL,8,Fwarehouse workers was not due to sex
OL,9,Fdiscrimination, as ITV News Reporter
OL,10,FCari Davies explains
OL,12,FThousands of former and current Next
OL,13,Femployees have won a landmark equal
OL,14,Fpay claim against the high street
OL,15,Fretailer after a six-year legal battle.
