OL,3,CThousands of Next retailer workers win
OL,4,Clandmark equal pay claim
OL,6,FUnder equal pay law, employees doing
OL,7,Fwork of equal value at the same
OL,8,Fcompany must be paid the same unless
OL,9,Fthe employer can show that any wage
OL,10,Fdifference is due to a "material
OL,11,Ffactor" unrelated to sex
OL,12,Fdiscrimination.
OL,14,FNext argued during the tribunal that
OL,15,Fthe wage difference between sales
OL,16,Fconsultants and warehouse operatives
OL,17,Fwas due to the different "market
OL,18,Frates" for these roles and was
OL,19,Fnecessary for the "viability" of the
OL,20,Fbusiness.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
