OL,3,CThousands of Next retailer workers win
OL,4,Clandmark equal pay claim
OL,6,FThis is the first equal pay claim of
OL,7,Fits kind against a British retailer to
OL,8,Fsecure a win, stated Leigh Day, the
OL,9,Flaw firm representing thousands of
OL,10,Fclaimants.
OL,12,FHelen Scarsbrook, 68, from Eastleigh
OL,13,Fnear Southampton, has worked for Next
OL,14,Ffor more than 20 years and was one of
OL,15,Fthree lead claimants representing all
OL,16,Fthe sales consultants in the claim.
OL,18,FShe said customer service was
OL,19,F"demanding" and often "undervalued".
