OL,6,FIn a statement issued through Leigh
OL,7,FDay, she said: "It has been a long six
OL,8,Fyears battling for the equal pay we
OL,9,Fall felt we rightly deserved but today
OL,10,Fwe can say we won.
OL,12,F"Anyone who works in retail knows that
OL,13,Fit is a physically and emotionally
OL,14,Ftough job.
OL,16,F"Customer service, in particular, is
OL,17,Fvery demanding and we do that in
OL,18,Faddition to lots of other essential
OL,19,Ftasks that go to make Next a
OL,20,Fsuccessful business.
OL,26,@oD@POUtD@AOUxD@AOU
