OL,6,F"You become so used to having your
OL,7,Fwork undervalued that you can easily
OL,8,Fstart to doubt it yourself.
OL,10,F"I am so grateful to the judges for
OL,11,Fseeing our jobs for what they really
OL,12,Fare ` equal."
OL,14,FNext has said it intends to appeal
OL,15,Fagainst the ruling.
