OL,6,FElizabeth George, Leigh Day's partner
OL,7,Fand barrister representing the
OL,8,Fsuccessful claimants, said the ruling
OL,9,Fwas "hugely significant" and the case
OL,10,Fwas "exactly the type of pay
OL,11,Fdiscrimination that equal pay
OL,12,Flegislation was intended to address".
OL,14,FShe continued: "When you have female-
OL,15,Fdominated jobs being paid less than
OL,16,Fmale-dominated jobs and the work is
OL,17,Fequal, employers cannot pay women less
OL,18,Fsimply by pointing to the market and
OL,19,Fsaying it is the going rate for the
OL,20,Fjobs. We knew that already.
OL,26,@qD@EOUqD@XO]rD@EOUtD@dO]vD@POU
