OL,3,CThousands of Next retailer workers win
OL,4,Clandmark equal pay claim
OL,6,F"The Employment Tribunal has confirmed
OL,7,Femployers must go further to justify
OL,8,Fpaying the different rates.
OL,10,F"They rightly found that Next could
OL,11,Fhave afforded to pay a higher rate but
OL,12,Fchose not to and that the reason for
OL,13,Fthat was purely financial.
OL,15,F"It is worth reminding people that the
OL,16,Ffinancial compensation they will now
OL,17,Fbe entitled to is not a windfall.
OL,19,F"It is pay that they were always
OL,20,Fentitled to if Next had complied with
OL,21,Fits equal pay obligations."
