OL,6,F"The tribunal expressed serious
OL,7,Fcriticisms of the claimants' expert
OL,8,Fevidence, and overwhelmingly accepted
OL,9,Fthe evidence of Next's expert and fact
OL,10,Fwitnesses.
OL,12,F"In respect of the specific terms in
OL,13,Fwhich the claim succeeded, it is our
OL,14,Fintention to appeal.
OL,16,F"This is the first equal pay group
OL,17,Faction in the private sector to reach
OL,18,Fa decision at tribunal level and
OL,19,Fraises a number of important points of
OL,20,Flegal principle."
