OL,6,FMore than 112,000 store staff across
OL,7,Fsupermarket chains Asda, Tesco,
OL,8,FSainsbury's, Morrisons and Co-op are
OL,9,Fbeing represented by Leigh Day
OL,10,Fbringing "similar equal pay claims,"
OL,11,Fthe law firm said.
OL,13,FNext operates 466 stores in the UK and
OL,14,Femploys 22,873 sales consultants.
OL,16,FIn 2023, the company's retail profits
OL,17,Fwere #241 million and its online
OL,18,Fprofits were #467 million, according
OL,19,Fto the ruling.
